.DESCRIPTION
The Get-PCAzureRateCard returns a list of Azure rates for the specified region.

.PARAMETER SaToken 
Specifies an authentication token with your Partner Center credentials.

.PARAMETER Region 
Specifies a two-character ISO 2 country code.

.PARAMETER Currency 
